Author:
Vol / Page:  332
Edition:  1950
Quote:  Mabel and I called on Wi Te Tahuhu ... and saw some 2000 tuna drying. ... I think there will be quite 20,000 eels in all for Te Whiti. Piripiri and Pene took a large contract from me[word missing???] fencing. They gave their word as Te Whiti men but would not sign an agreement.
