Author:
Vol / Page:  2
Edition:
Quote:  I do not know whether you heard the story about a Nelson woman beseeching Mr. Mackay to give up the pakehas and go and live at Parihaka, for Te Whiti had told his people that all the Europeans would be destroyed, and she begged her old friend to embrace Te Whiti-ism while there was yet time.
